  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Ending Agriculture Bonded Labour in Nepal</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">ActionAid International Nepal has signed MOU with The Freedom Fund to Implement 3 Years long project titled &#x201C;Ending Agriculture Bonded Labour in Nepal (EABL)&quot; in Nepal. The overall goal of the project is a significant reduction in the prevalence of agricultural bonded labour in Nepal and survivors accessing sustainable freedom by receiving support for recovery and long-term resilience against exploitation. The project will take place in a post-Covid-19 context and adjust to the pandemic impact on these communities and the movement to end agricultural bonded labour.</narrative>
  </description>
